data.title: Intellistake Strengthens AI Infrastructure Platform With Entry Into Space-Based Data Centers
data.description: Intellistake Technologies Corp. (CSE: ISTK) (OTCQB: ISTKF) (FSE: E41) ("Intellistake" or the "Company") is highlighting how its partnership and strategic investment in Orbit AI1 positions the Company at the infrastructure layer of what it sees as the next phase of cloud and AI – data centers and verification systems that operate in space, as well as on Earth.
